I think `resourceLimits` is always present but each property may be missing (you get `{}` if no limit was given).
Therefore change `ResourceLimits ` also to
```
interface ResourceLimits {
    maxYoungGenerationSizeMb?: number;
    maxOldGenerationSizeMb?: number;
    codeRangeSizeMb?: number;
}
```
Once again this fits fine to options as the whole `resourceLimits` property is optional but if it is present each limit property is optional.

